      <prefercite id="aspace_167d7847ca312d9bf42e910be5246dc1">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Dean Sakamoto Collection of Yale School of Architecture Exhibition Publications, Robert B. Haas Family Arts Library, Yale University.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <bioghist id="aspace_8fc9074c5a4f40389f3268ae5f60dc02">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Dean Sakamoto is a practicing architect and a critic at the Yale School of Architecture. He was Director of Exhibitions for the School's gallery from 1999 to 2011.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_457b5c599dac9e5b90f50a6b6fbae151">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection contains 36 selected publications which were published during Dean Sakamoto's tenure as Director of Exhibitions for the Yale School of Architecture.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_dbb30d8ba8f8711a0f79ed517212a32e">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Arranged in reverse chronological order.</p>  
      </arrangement>
